src: Ocús is sí in Flidhais sín máthair Níadh Ségamain maic Adamair, ⁊ do bhlightheá a flaith Niadh Ségamhain in búar sin .i. diabúlbhúar .i. bá ⁊ eillti do bhliaghan re linn Níad Ségamain, ⁊ issí a máthair túc in cúmhachta t-sidhamail sin dó.

masked: Galanga lang .i. fell, goa .i. breg .i. Cormac mac Taidhg meic Ceín dorinne gó frisna brocaibh .i [MASK] gai Táidhg rug Cormac laís chum na m-broc ar co tísdaís asa m-broicthenaigh amach ar enech Taidhg [MASK] Céin [MASK] ⁊ [MASK] Taidhg ag Cormac do chomartha [MASK].
src: Galanga lang .i. fell, goa .i. breg .i. Cormac mac Taidhg meic Ceín dorinne gó frisna brocaibh .i. gai Táidhg rug Cormac laís chum na m-broc ar co tísdaís asa m-broicthenaigh amach ar enech Taidhg meic Céin, ⁊ gaí Taidhg ag Cormac do chomartha friú.

src: Tainic dono Mogh Ruith anuas iarsin ⁊ dodechaid a n-a charpat caemh cumdachta for damaibh dreamhna dasachtaca cu luas gaeithi Marta con athlaime ethaiti ⁊ seche thairbh maeil uidhir lais ⁊ tainic i remtus rompa ⁊ do chuir Cennmhar uatha do gresacht fer Muman ⁊ tancatar co hescad i lenmain in druadh

masked: Is ann immurro celebrait na cristaide líth ⁊ sollamain a etsechta Coluim Cille h-i quint id Iuin arái lathi mis gréne cecha bliadne [MASK] lathi-se indiu ⁊ & rl [MASK] Ndisit immurro ecnaide na [MASK] ind inbuid-sin cecha bliadne becan cumbair don foilsiugud socheneoil ⁊ særchlandachta noim Choluim Cille ⁊ dino dona fertaib ⁊ dona mirbulib díairmide do-roine in [MASK] aire i fus isin t-sægul ⁊ don forbai [MASK] [MASK] forciund t-sainemail [MASK] [MASK] deoid for a rith [MASK].i. rochtain co a fir-athardai ocus co [MASK] fir-duchus fen .i. co h-attreb parrduis i frecnarcus De co sír
src: Is ann immurro celebrait na cristaide líth ⁊ sollamain a etsechta Coluim Cille h-i quint id Iuin arái lathi mis gréne cecha bliadne isin lathi-se indiu ⁊ &rl I Ndisit immurro ecnaide na n-Goedel ind inbuid-sin cecha bliadne becan cumbair don foilsiugud socheneoil ⁊ særchlandachta noim Choluim Cille ⁊ dino dona fertaib ⁊ dona mirbulib díairmide do-roine in Coimdíu aire i fus isin t-sægul ⁊ don forbai ⁊ don forciund t-sainemail do-rat fa deoid for a rith m-bvadai .i. rochtain co a fir-athardai ocus co a fir-duchus fen .i. co h-attreb parrduis i frecnarcus De co sír

src: A inde beus ataat a tuided, doaithnet, doaidbed, doiagod, A airpert .i. atat a n-aigne .i. na guta ⁊ na consaine: dotuidhet uait a lipriph uaid a litrib .i. tinntaidhid asinn aignedh sin i litriph: doaithnet asna litriph sin i bfoclaiph: dotiagat asna foclaib sin a sretha rosga ⁊ fasaigh ⁊ airchetail on filidecht .i. ros eolus ⁊ sgoth indsgi .i. indsge eolais: doaitbet .i. doaisbenad d'eochtaiph .i. a ciall ⁊ a caireachtaire .i. fuatha na litrech: no go mad totus a bunad Laitne in focail is atat ud docent ali.

src: Conchubar Abhradrúadh .i. rosc rúadh co mailgibh rúadha ro thecht, nam brai mala dicitur.

src: Ro gab dono in chaillech na runnu remráidte i fiadnaise Ghuaire

src: Brénainn Biorra,

src: Cearttharsna ar aicme ailme .i. aenmer ar in cetfidh na n-aicme, a dho ar in fid tanaise, co soised a coig ar in coiged fid secip aicme.

src: Drong in so, senchas nád oll, fri tuirim lúad Lagenglonn, ní éicsem h-uile do glé cid fri sægul sechtmaine.

src: Reim dano .i. raid uaim intan is phrois.

src: Ruidlius do filidecht a preith re sechta.

src: Deich céd cenn tosach bar n-áir, timchell ríg Ulad ollbáin; d'fheraib Alban sin san ár, ⁊ fiche céd comlán.

Turnae, gurab [MASK] féin do ruc an dá chuileán chon sin a ttigh Fearghusa Finnléith an uair do [MASK] sí [MASK] coin [MASK].
src: Agus a ndiaigh na slána sin do daingniughadh tucc si fleasc dhoilbhthi draoidheachta óna cuim ⁊ do bhúail in chú dhí ⁊ dorine ríogan cruthach chaomh-álainn di; ⁊ do innis in ríogan .i. Turnae, gurab í féin do ruc an dá chuileán chon sin a ttigh Fearghusa Finnléith an uair do bhí sí 'na coin ann.

src: Co tarut airdhi na crochi do láim na nóiden darsin talmain co r-rímaid topur usci ass

src: Duibsinaig.

src: Hisindfirmimint cogle sesca dáse senistre, dothaitni fridia 'malle cachphairti se senistre.

src: a Clanna Eoghuin arm-ruaidh.

src: Fothad Cairpthech isbreth dó ainm .i. issed slaibhri coníredh, mairc cona cairpthibh.

src: Percoba, cainiu cachfiach, setig Noe meicc Lamhiach, mna natrimac, monar ngle Olla, Oliua, Oliuane.

src: Nogésed fo cech ríg nogébad Érinn.

src: Ba holc lia Díen Cécht an freapaid-sin.

src: Is de bá Níadh in Chairn Cormac.

src: Atbert-sum, ‘Atom-athcomairc,’ ol sé, ‘Im corrguinech.’

src: Toet in og isin dún

src: Is aire sin atberthe ‘Sírna Saeghlach’ dé.

masked: is e in [MASK] ⁊ Is etargaire dno eter [MASK] ⁊ mascul insin: no is etargaire intan [MASK] fri neach n-aili co n-anmairm a athar senrud.
src: is e in fear ⁊ Is etargaire dno eter fhemem ⁊ mascul insin: no is etargaire intan deifriche fri neach n-aili co n-anmairm a athar senrud.

src: Benais Patraic a chlocc co cualatar fir Erenn itir biu ⁊ marbu

masked: Agus do ghluais misi fón doire ann sin, ⁊ do dhúiscighius an lon ⁊ do reathus ris [MASK] do ghabhus é ⁊ [MASK] d'Aoife é; ⁊ arna thabairt [MASK], [MASK] eadh adubhairt:
src: Agus do ghluais misi fón doire ann sin, ⁊ do dhúiscighius an lon ⁊ do reathus ris ⁊ do ghabhus é ⁊ tucus d'Aoife é; ⁊ arna thabairt dí, as eadh adubhairt:

masked: Ro gab imorro ingean Engist for dail na fleidhi .i. fina [MASK] siccera a leastraib oir ⁊ [MASK] comtar mesgda meadarchain na sluaig; do cuaid tra demon i n-Gortigernn im ghrad [MASK] Engist ⁊ [MASK] [MASK] berlaidh dia saigid dia cuinge d'on rig do h-Engist ⁊ ro [MASK] cidbe cungeas 'na tochra do bearthar do
src: Ro gab imorro ingean Engist for dail na fleidhi .i. fina ⁊ siccera a leastraib oir ⁊ airgid comtar mesgda meadarchain na sluaig; do cuaid tra demon i n-Gortigernn im ghrad ingeine Engist ⁊ rola in berlaidh dia saigid dia cuinge d'on rig do h-Engist ⁊ ro raid cidbe cungeas 'na tochra do bearthar do

masked: Silad clann dono do rad o uir in talman do radh frisin fid n-ogaim rogab [MASK] fria .i. [MASK] cechtar de.
src: Silad clann dono do rad o uir in talman do radh frisin fid n-ogaim rogab comainm fria .i. ur cechtar de.

masked: .i. [MASK] remur medón a mhuineóil.
src: .i. bá remur medón a mhuineóil.

masked: Do-chualaid dono Aedan mac Colmain a fuair Cormac d'onoir ⁊ tanic [MASK] dichur Cormaic ⁊ ad-bert [MASK] comad h-e Fidchuri mac Airt Chuirp ⁊ tuc fearand d'Aedan ⁊ adubairt [MASK] re Cormac Tir Luigne do fhacbail ⁊ adubairt: [MASK] in do Leith Cuind tu a Cormaic?’ ar Aedan ⁊ [MASK] Diarmaid: ‘beirmaid sib [MASK] acalad
src: Do-chualaid dono Aedan mac Colmain a fuair Cormac d'onoir ⁊ tanic do dichur Cormaic ⁊ ad-bert aroili comad h-e Fidchuri mac Airt Chuirp ⁊ tuc fearand d'Aedan ⁊ adubairt Aedan re Cormac Tir Luigne do fhacbail ⁊ adubairt:‘in do Leith Cuind tu a Cormaic?’ ar Aedan ⁊ adubairt Diarmaid: ‘beirmaid sib araen acalad

src: Inrí reil narun corath doarfaid dún cachn-ingnad, diathuicsin treothu, din ngle, is trialin amirbaile.

src: Tritreba condéni anair greni friturcbail toebdein, isatrí dondleith aniar frisreith, frifuiniud fírian.

masked: Ocus ro [MASK] a sliocht [MASK] clochaib ocus i talmain re ré cian re drecma na h-érma co raibe spunc áiblech teined [MASK] t-aer dar a n-éise tra [MASK] rucad ar Chuan Fithise ann sin
src: Ocus ro búi a sliocht i clochaib ocus i talmain re ré cian re drecma na h-érma co raibe spunc áiblech teined in t-aer dar a n-éise tra acht rucad ar Chuan Fithise ann sin

src: Ri rodelb eisse cachnduil rosderb cengesse coemruin, eter mín isgarb condath, eter marb ocus beothach.

src: is uad Cethei.

src: O ro fhothaig Colum Cille h-Íí luid for cuairt a procepta fo Albain ⁊ Bretnu ⁊ Saxanchu co nus-tuc dócum n-irsi ⁊ cretmi iar fertaib ilib do dénum do iar todúscad marb a bás

masked: [MASK] marbad tra amlaid Suibne Menn le Mael Coba mac Fiacha rí Ulad i g-ciunn [MASK] m-bliadan déc la Conghal Claen mac Scannláin ro-cher ocus ní la Mael Coba mac [MASK]

masked: Níor faillaigheadh sin leision; do éirghe ina sheasamh ⁊ [MASK] [MASK] a mhéar [MASK] suathnimh [MASK] sleighi sith-fhoda do bhí [MASK] ⁊ tuc rogha n-urchuir dí, gur chuir ceand na sleighi tar in macaomh ⁊ gur bhúail crand na [MASK] ar droim a chind siar seachtair, gur [MASK] coimreamhar an craind d'feilbh reamhair fair, gur chuir an tsleagh a talmain feadh láimhe laoich don taoibh eile de .’
src: Níor faillaigheadh sin leision; do éirghe ina sheasamh ⁊ do chuir a mhéar a suathnimh na sleighi sith-fhoda do bhí aige ⁊ tuc rogha n-urchuir dí, gur chuir ceand na sleighi tar in macaomh ⁊ gur bhúail crand na sleighi ar droim a chind siar seachtair, gur fágadh coimreamhar an craind d'feilbh reamhair fair, gur chuir an tsleagh a talmain feadh láimhe laoich don taoibh eile de.’

src: Ro marbtha dna iartain Tuatha Fidhbha

src: Tancatar sruthi Erenn aidchi co salmu ⁊ imannaib ⁊ ni thesta forru in t-sollsi nach in bolad angelacda

src: Cárthend is Fiachra co ngail is in t-anrád Amalgaid.

src: Ícais an gillai tre inndeld a eladon.

src: Cú mac Ferghusa .i. Conmac a ainm ⁊ Lugaid Conmac ainm aile dó.

src: Cuig meic la Domnall, Gilliberd, ri O Maini, ocus Dauith, ocus Tadg Mor Catha Atha na Righ, ocus Concobar, ri O Maine, ocus Aed; ocus nir b'inann mathair leo, acht le dis, Tadg, ocus Conchobar;

masked: Ni thic don [MASK] tacras tu [MASK] na tri [MASK] Art It fir-aithesc ni ba brec Va dire à [MASK] armées ô Cecht que chacun d'eux dira dans la suite: ‘olc in turas tancamar’
src: Ni thic don tshuagh tacras tu freacra na tri coicead Art It fir-aithesc ni ba brec Va dire à tes armées ô Cecht que chacun d'eux dira dans la suite: ‘olc in turas tancamar’

src: Geibed cách a dréchta de —is ed téchta in túaslaicthe.

src: Is ed onn iar n-aicneadh ail, Is i in cloch iar saerdataid.

src: 'Mannerat cachni 'sinbiuth imdochlaind, imdochiniud, icathaib garbaib cenchleith, ingalraib, itedmannaib'

src: Nó Eogan-necht .i. necht Eogain .i. necht clann .i. clann Eogain na secht n-Éoghanachta.

src: Neim nathrach, eghad and 'na sgriphend.

src: ‘Is cia son ger fogabar O nach fuach tren tindscanar?’ .i. ernin getal.

src: ‘A fir shochuir’ ar siat ‘ga ret sut doni Leth Cuind?’

src: Nó didiu is ó Chuillinn Murthemne rohainmnighedh.

src: A mboí íerum og imdect co n-acu an n-ingen foro cind go ndeilb nderscoighte.

src: Amail is neimneach dubh in dáel la cách is mar sin bat neimhnech goirtbhriathrach ó erlabhra intí Dubthach fri cach n-aen.

src: Is andsin ro chan Sinech in molad-sa do Diarmait:

src: Ata saer lenn cenu .i. Luchtai mac Luachadhae.’

masked: Ruidlius intan raiter [MASK] is e bel no fiacail an fir: no ruidlius is se an fer so, cona anmaim [MASK].
src: Ruidlius intan raiter, is e bel no fiacail an fir: no ruidlius is se an fer so, cona anmaim saindredaig.

src: Is amlaid sin deiligter feudha et forfeudha ⁊ taophoumna.

src: Iontóigheas Díorraing mur a raibhe Fionn ⁊ d'innis sin dó.

src: Tíagait na filid ina díaid; atchí Congal na filidu chuici ⁊ as-bert:

masked: Meic Iareth, [MASK] [MASK], meic maith molbthaig Malalíal, meic Cainain, meic Enos ail, meic Seth saindil, meic Adaim.
src: Meic Iareth, tomthaib triath, meic maith molbthaig Malalíal, meic Cainain, meic Enos ail, meic Seth saindil, meic Adaim.

masked: Cuirche cendmar ba rí rot for Medraige is [MASK] Herot; is lais ná fúair fóesam fír Blod [MASK] Con meic Caiss clothmín
src: Cuirche cendmar ba rí rot for Medraige is for Herot; is lais ná fúair fóesam fír Blod mac Con meic Caiss clothmín

masked: mochur domaig nimi [MASK], mabith fothrúaigi digraid.
src: mochur domaig nimi nair, mabith fothrúaigi digraid.

masked: Atbert ant athair, ‘Cisí écin det-bert asin tír [MASK] forgabais?’
src: Atbert ant athair, ‘Cisí écin det-bert asin tír hi forgabais?’

masked: Adba [MASK], ilar phian, mairg bís fócrithfeidm comchian, glenn [MASK], gann, gráne ali, morí rogmar dorigni.
src: Adba n-Iffirn, ilar phian, mairg bís fócrithfeidm comchian, glenn golmar, gann, gráne ali, morí rogmar dorigni.

masked: Do dhligegaibh [MASK] na nduan inso sis.
src: Do dhligegaibh dunta na nduan inso sis.

masked: [MASK] didiu ann, [MASK] ríg, ar mo dúthaig do thabairt dam in tan bud [MASK] for Érinn tusa ⁊ níro airisius co h-Ailech Néit, ar is ann [MASK] domnás in ríg in tan sin .’
src: Do-deachusa didiu ann, a ríg, ar mo dúthaig do thabairt dam in tan bud ríg for Érinn tusa ⁊ níro airisius co h-Ailech Néit, ar is ann buí domnás in ríg in tan sin.’

masked: [MASK] eim banindsge for ferindsge intan isberar ‘is i [MASK] gobur,’:
src: Fedhair eim banindsge for ferindsge intan isberar ‘is i in gobur,’:

masked: Berthuss iarum in mac ⁊ ad-bail Daire ⁊ berid nai m-bretha iarna gein fo chetoir [MASK]. ‘Do-leic for lar [MASK] ar a mathair
src: Berthuss iarum in mac ⁊ ad-bail Daire ⁊ berid nai m-bretha iarna gein fo chetoir .i. ‘Do-leic for lar’ ar a mathair

src: Fecht n-aon do luid Aodh Dorndine ben Néill Frasaig do ordugud ríghe Cairnd Ólnécmachta

masked: — ‘Beiridh beannachtain’ ar se ‘[MASK] da mad ead no [MASK] agaibh a foiditin no raghuinn-si uaibh [MASK] na cluinfind a foraithmet cu brath?’
src: — ‘Beiridh beannachtain’ ar se ‘ar da mad ead no beith agaibh a foiditin no raghuinn-si uaibh ait na cluinfind a foraithmet cu brath?’

masked: Ocus ro-ráidhe Seachnall ba córu [MASK] eich uccut [MASK] breith dond espug do Fíiac.
src: Ocus ro-ráidhe Seachnall ba córu ind eich uccut do breith dond espug do Fíiac.

masked: Ní racha díbh [MASK] andsa rígthech nemda.
src: Ní racha díbh ænnech andsa rígthech nemda.

masked: ‘Clocha’ [MASK] in fer
src: ‘Clocha’ or in fer

masked: Iar sin trá bátar Lagin im [MASK] ocon cháiniud.
src: Iar sin trá bátar Lagin im Rónán ocon cháiniud.

masked: Tucad uad-side fora fidh coibnesa [MASK] ogaim.
src: Tucad uad-side fora fidh coibnesa in ogaim.

masked: Ocus ro érig in gilla cédna doridisi .i [MASK] Gáir Gann ⁊ as-bert in cédna fri Congal ut [MASK]
src: Ocus ro érig in gilla cédna doridisi .i. Gáir Gann ⁊ as-bert in cédna fri Congal ut:

masked: [MASK] ua h-Ebricc in [MASK] is é ro-sáruigh Etan ingean Dián Cécht at brú Boínne gu rus-toirrchiustur, co-toracht Oengus iar sain gurro-marb Abcán.
src: Abcán ua h-Ebricc in file is é ro-sáruigh Etan ingean Dián Cécht at brú Boínne gu rus-toirrchiustur, co-toracht Oengus iar sain gurro-marb Abcán.

masked: Do-níat na [MASK] a n-áentaidh iarsin.
src: Do-níat na clérigh a n-áentaidh iarsin.

masked: Ne a airichill .i. calaidh nem ind usce, [MASK] nem nathrach
src: Ne a airichill .i. calaidh nem ind usce, no nem nathrach

masked: Leagar duinne [MASK] ar tri righ Corca Laoighdhe Flann ⁊ [MASK] ⁊ Eidirscel or is rinn [MASK] adhbhar ar techt co h-Inis Clere da rucsat ar mna ⁊ ar maccaeimh a m-broid ⁊ ni tharramar iat re dhigail forru ⁊ gabhmait-ne [MASK] laim [MASK] aniugh.
src: Leagar duinne iat ar tri righ Corca Laoighdhe Flann ⁊ Cobhthach ⁊ Eidirscel or is rinn do-ronsad adhbhar ar techt co h-Inis Clere da rucsat ar mna ⁊ ar maccaeimh a m-broid ⁊ ni tharramar iat re dhigail forru ⁊ gabhmait-ne do laim iat-somh aniugh.

masked: Nir 'bho follus doibh [MASK] fo a ghabhuil, ⁊ ni fhaictis ní tairis [MASK]
src: Nir 'bho follus doibh ní fo a ghabhuil, ⁊ ni fhaictis ní tairis.

masked: Crithinbél .i [MASK] bél na chrither .i. ara neimhnighe ⁊ ara theintemhlacht na m-bríathar úadh, [MASK] is nemhnech bríathra in dána iter.
src: Crithinbél .i. bél na chrither .i. ara neimhnighe ⁊ ara theintemhlacht na m-bríathar úadh, ar is nemhnech bríathra in dána iter.

masked: I Arsain tic [MASK] asintsruth, bai fortir 'cotirmugud, dosfánic nél [MASK] cotarmairt héc cenanmain.
src: I Arsain tic Euá asintsruth, bai fortir 'cotirmugud, dosfánic nél iarsétsain cotarmairt héc cenanmain.

masked: Brisis in tonn in cathbarr ⁊ tocaib suas in [MASK] in mac co n-acatar a gnuis for barr [MASK] tuindi
src: Brisis in tonn in cathbarr ⁊ tocaib suas in tond in mac co n-acatar a gnuis for barr na tuindi
